OL,5, The boss of British Gas owner Centrica 
OL,6, has told the BBC his pay last year of  
OL,7, #4.5m is "impossible to justify".      
OL,9,FChris O'Shea described the package of  
OL,10,Fsalary, bonus and shares as a huge     
OL,11,Famount of money and said he was        
OL,12,Fincredibly fortunate.                  
